image= cv2.cvtColor(Circles, cv2.COLOR_BGR2RGB)

img = cv2.threshold(Circles, 127, 255, cv2.THRESH_BINARY)[1]
output = cv2.connectedComponentsWithStats(img, 8, cv2.CV_32S)
